Competition: Copa Libertadores
Season: 1960

*Teams: Peñarol (Uruguay), Millonarios (Colombia), Olimpia (Paraguay), San Lorenzo (Argentina), Esporte Clube Bahia (Brasil), Jorge Wilstermann (Bolivia), Universidad de Chile (Chile). The champion national teams of Ecuador, Peru and Venezuela did not participate in the first edition.
 
